&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VScode 下载地址：&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://code.visualstudio.com&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://code.visualstudio.com&lt;/a&gt;


